  "content_id": "71da4a85-2c2a-4c22-ba6d-9b1b4a832010",
  "description": "Helplines providing advice and support to the families of people in prison - including the Prisoners' Families Helpline",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Get support and advice if you know someone in prison.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"prisons-in-england-and-wales\">Prisons in England and Wales</h2>\n\n<p>You can contact:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Prisoners’ Families Helpline <br>\n<a href=\"mailto:info@prisonersfamilies.org\">info@prisonersfamilies.org</a><br>\nTelephone: 0808 808 2003</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"prisons-in-scotland\">Prisons in Scotland</h2>\n\n<p>You can contact:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Families Outside Support and Information Helpline <br>\nTelephone: 0800 254 0088<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"prisons-in-northern-ireland\">Prisons in Northern Ireland</h2>\n\n<p>You can <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.niacro.co.uk/family-links\">find information about how to access the Family Links service</a>.</p>\n\n<p>You can also get help and advice from:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.prisonersfamilies.org/\">Prisoners’ Families Helpline website</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.partnersofprisoners.co.uk/\">Partners of Prisoners and Families Support Group</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.prisonadvice.org.uk/\">Prison Advice and Care Trust (PACT)</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.prisonreformtrust.org.uk/\">Prison Reform Trust</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
